name: Stellenbosch Developer Meetup
body:
### Welcome to the rough draft.
We hope to do a lot for the community and the developer culture in Stellenbosch and in the rest of South Africa! 

If you are new here feel free to leave a message or come talk to us in person at any of our Bi-Monthly Meetups!

### Developer Goals
We hope to grow as a group and in doing so grow the scale of future projects. 
Our goal will be to give experienced developers a place to come and share ideas 
while new people come to learn valuable skills and create interesting projects.

### More than just code.
Strive to go the extra mile and accommodate many different aspects of Tech, by giving the opportunity for anyone to
talk about their new Idea/App/hobby. 

### Meet up locations and times to be announced here
Watch this space
